\title{Magic World Watch Deploy}

\taxon{skill}

\meta{description}{Build, deploy, and manage the MagicWorldWatch iOS/watchOS voice-to-task pipeline app. Use when building for device or simulator, fixing Xcode project issues, or running the 7-world backend pipeline.}

